Package: abtest
Title: Calculate A/B Test Results Using Bayesian Methods
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("W. Jake", "Thompson", , "wjakethompson@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7339-0300"))
  )
Description: Calculate the results of an A/B test using Bayesian methods. Use
    rstanarm to interface with 'Stan' and estimate the difference between to
    conditions. Visualize the results using a Shiny application.
